  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Last Group Out</strong> is a casual top-down extraction shooter set in a collapsed society where only survival matters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by \"Escape from Tarkov\" and \"The Escapists\".</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Scavenge & Survive</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter a hostile, abandoned land teeming with danger and opportunity.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grab what you can before time runs out, or risk losing it all.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your loot runs to level up, grow your wealth, and prepare for greater threats.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Loot, Sell, Upgrade</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find gear, weapons, and oddities scattered across the wasteland.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sell what you don’t need to buy stronger equipment.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize and enhance your weapons with powerful buffs.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843730/extras/07b00fcfd1d1f5e973dc5f992daad6c4.poster.avif?t=1771138953\" width=360 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843730/extras/07b00fcfd1d1f5e973dc5f992daad6c4.webm?t=1771138953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843730/extras/07b00fcfd1d1f5e973dc5f992daad6c4.mp4?t=1771138953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Level Up & Evolve</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gain XP by defeating enemies, looting gear, and completing quests.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new weapons, equipment, and boss challenges.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your loadout to match your playstyle: stealthy, aggressive, or something in between. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843730/extras/09254f8d58ab12b96c98b5683c905eda.poster.avif?t=1771138953\" width=240 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843730/extras/09254f8d58ab12b96c98b5683c905eda.webm?t=1771138953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843730/extras/09254f8d58ab12b96c98b5683c905eda.mp4?t=1771138953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Use All Your Senses</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Danger lurks in every shadow.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stop. Look. Listen. Smell.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your instincts and stealth to stay one step ahead of enemies and rivals.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Solo or Co-op</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go it alone, or team up with up to 3 friends.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on missions, level up, and extract with hard-earned loot, together.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Last Group Out</strong> is a casual top-down extraction shooter set in a collapsed society where only survival matters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by \"Escape from Tarkov\" and \"The Escapists\".</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Scavenge & Survive</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter a hostile, abandoned land teeming with danger and opportunity.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grab what you can before time runs out, or risk losing it all.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your loot runs to level up, grow your wealth, and prepare for greater threats.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Loot, Sell, Upgrade</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find gear, weapons, and oddities scattered across the wasteland.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sell what you don’t need to buy stronger equipment.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize and enhance your weapons with powerful buffs.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843730/extras/07b00fcfd1d1f5e973dc5f992daad6c4.poster.avif?t=1771138953\" width=360 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843730/extras/07b00fcfd1d1f5e973dc5f992daad6c4.webm?t=1771138953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843730/extras/07b00fcfd1d1f5e973dc5f992daad6c4.mp4?t=1771138953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Level Up & Evolve</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gain XP by defeating enemies, looting gear, and completing quests.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new weapons, equipment, and boss challenges.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your loadout to match your playstyle: stealthy, aggressive, or something in between. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843730/extras/09254f8d58ab12b96c98b5683c905eda.poster.avif?t=1771138953\" width=240 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843730/extras/09254f8d58ab12b96c98b5683c905eda.webm?t=1771138953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843730/extras/09254f8d58ab12b96c98b5683c905eda.mp4?t=1771138953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Use All Your Senses</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Danger lurks in every shadow.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stop. Look. Listen. Smell.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your instincts and stealth to stay one step ahead of enemies and rivals.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Solo or Co-op</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go it alone, or team up with up to 3 friends.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on missions, level up, and extract with hard-earned loot, together.</p></li></ul>",
